We'll especially talk about how they
exist in two different general areas.

27
00:01:02,225 --> 00:01:05,280
Well-formed problem domains that
have a well-structured problem and

28
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,510
a correct answer.

29
00:01:06,510 --> 00:01:09,460
And more poorly from problem
domains where the things to

30
00:01:09,460 --> 00:01:12,550
learn are a little bit more fuzzy, and
